{"title":"旧胡同新面貌（图片）","authors":["邵宇"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":9,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧胡同新面貌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（首都速写之十）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵宇作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“无风三尺土，下雨满街泥。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧北京就这样对待劳动人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳快落西的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这胡同又到了赌钱、酗酒、婆婆骂媳妇、丈夫打老婆、孩子要饭吃的时候了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在一切都变样了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡同干净了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户订了爱国公约，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了新的娱乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办了成人夜校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王府井的自来水也流过来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑板报上写着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱国增产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人勤劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗美援朝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捐献飞机大炮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那远远的城根上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一所新房在建造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古老的城墙别傲骄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新楼要比旧城高！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}